              Diseño moderno y responsive
            </p>
          </div>

          <div
            class="w-full flex gap-4 text-grisClaro font-Poppins uppercase items-center py-4 border-b border-acento/30 group hover:border-primario"
          >
            <span class="text-[12px] group-hover:text-secundario">06</span>
            <p class="text-base font-bold group-hover:text-blanco lg:text-6xl">
